<h1>Dossiers</h1>
<p>A readable write-up of each mark's validity checks &mdash; the design, the effect with its uncertainty split,
   the full validity battery, and the provenance. A mark is included only if it passes these checks.</p>
<div class="cards">
  {{range .Marks}}
  <div class="card">
    <span class="domain">{{.Domain}} · {{.UnitType}}</span>
    <h3>{{.Series}}</h3>
    <p>{{.Estimand}}</p>
    <span class="effect">Effect {{.EffectStr}} · {{.Status}}</span>
    <a class="more" href="{{.ID}}.html">Open dossier &rarr;</a>
  </div>
  {{end}}
</div>
